title: ICSI CSEET June 2026 Enrollment Window Now Open
content:
# ICSI CSEET June 2026 Enrollment Window Now Open

Ek important update hai Company Secretary aspirants ke liye! The Institute of Company Secretaries of India (ICSI) ne Company Secretary Executive Entrance Test (CSEET) June 2026 session ke liye enrollment process commence kar diya hai, as of March 1, 2026. Jo students June 2026 exams mein appear hona chahte hain, unke liye enrollment dates announce ho chuki hain.

*   **Enrollment Start Date:** March 01, 2026.
*   **Last Date for Enrollment (without late fee):** April 07, 2026.
*   **Last Date for Enrollment (with late fee):** April 20, 2026.
*   **Eligibility:** Only those candidates who successfully registered for the CSEET June 2026 session by February 28, 2026, are eligible to enroll for the examination.
*   **Examination Dates:** The CSEET June 2026 examination is scheduled to be conducted from June 01, 2026, to June 04, 2026.

## Read the Official Document
*   [Download the Official Notification/Circular here](https://www.icsi.edu/media/webmodules/CSEET-CutOff-Dates-2026.pdf)

*Published on: 1 March 2026*
